data.description: This open concept, 4 bed, 3 full bath home is in the PERFECT location & has all of the upgrades and features you've been looking for! The home sits right in front of a beautifully maintained park, is near restaurants, Fort Bliss, shopping and so much more. The dream kitchen boasts an extra large granite island, stainless steel appliances, crown molding around the skylight and extra cabinet space! The home features crown molding, shutters, granite, and so much more throughout. There is a barn door separating the front 2 bedrooms and bath from the the rest of the home (perfect for guests or as an in-law suite!) All 4 bedrooms are spacious. The front, back, and side yard all feature synthetic turf landscaping. Garage features an added window and door to the secluded & landscaped (turf and cement) side yard. You have to check it out! Call listing agents with any questions.
